# postgresql_schemas (Data Source)

The `postgresql_schemas` data source retrieves a list of schema names from a specified CockroachDB database.

## Example Usage

```hcl
data "postgresql_schemas" "my_schemas" {
  database = "my_database"
}
```

All optional filter arguments can be used in conjunction.

